As an AI language model, I don't have personal preferences, but here are some famous landmarks that are worth visiting:

1. The Eiffel Tower in Paris
2. Machu Picchu in Peru
3. The Taj Mahal in India
4. The Great Wall of China in China
5. The Colosseum in Rome
6. The Statue of Liberty in New York
7. The Pyramids of Giza in Egypt
8. The Great Barrier Reef in Australia
9. Petra in Jordan

Ultimately, the landmarks you choose to visit will depend on your personal interests and location. It's always best to research the landmarks in the area you're traveling to and determine which ones you're most interested in seeing.
